[Masamune] Thank you. But I didn't know they were
selling sandwiches.

[Elena] But since the quantity is limited, it's a
competition.
[Elena] We don't get supplies every day either.

[Elena] I used to be able to buy them with
privileges at the magic club, but I quit already.

[Elena] Masamune, you know about Elena and the
Magic Club too, huh?
[Masamune] I don't really care about Elena's past.

[Masamune] Elena is strong. She stood up to
Jackson properly.

[Masamune] Ah, I fought against Jackson who was
trying to summon a demon at first.
[Masamune] Elena also had an amazing performance.

[Masamune] It feels strange that I'm the only one
who knows things that Elena doesn't know.

[Elena] Tell me everything. It's unfair that only
Masamune knows.

[Elena] Elena also wants to know more about
Masamune.

[Elena] Reverse rape in the Magic Research
Dungeon... I heard about it yesterday, but to
actually say it out loud, it's shocking...

[Masamune] I was completely at the mercy of three
gyarus.
[Masamune] It's fine. Now it's just a good memory.

[Elena] Hmm, that's not fair! Elena also wants to
have sex with Masamune.

[Masamune] It's still just temporary... so it's
too early for that kind of thing.

[Masamune] (If even Elena is disappointed in
me...)

[Elena] ...  Note: The translation for this line
is simply ... as it represents a pause or silence
in the dialogue.

[Elena] By the way, you're doing other things too,
right?

[Elena] I'm not blaming you or anything. Elena
can't really say anything about others either.

[Masamune] I won't do it anymore. I have a
girlfriend too.

[Elena] Yeah... but it's still just temporary,
though.

StudentWhat do you think of my magic circle? The

of magical power, so the bigger it is, the more
skilled a magician I am.

the school last night was arrested. It's scary,
isn't it?

StudentN-No... my panties... they're... ahh, it

MasamuneThere was a senior girl who was stealing

Thank you. I was about to start hating all the

StudentI bought new panties. The boys will never

StudentWhat... wait, those are my panties! Why

MasamuneUm... I bought them from Senpai...
